      "cooked": "<p>Teatri Kombetar sjell ne skene premieren me te re, “Opera per 3 grosh”, kryevepra e autorit çek, Vaclav Havel. Vepra që është shkruar në vitin 1972 ka ende nota fort aktuale në vendin tonë.<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/original/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6.JPG\" data-download-href=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6\" title=\"IMG_3194.JPG\"><img src=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6_2_387x800.JPG\" width=\"387\" height=\"800\" srcset=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6_2_387x800.JPG, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6_2_580x1200.JPG 1.5x, https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6_2_774x1600.JPG 2x\" data-small-upload=\"https://peshkupauje.com/uploads/default/optimized/2X/1/1e46c001bb7b4cc1dd857f6dc0c63fc230c6e9e6_2_10x10.png\"><div class=\"meta\">\n<svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_3194.JPG</span><span class=\"informations\">945×1950 2.44 MB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use xlink:href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg>\n</div></a></div>Vjen prej dates 9-10-11 Dhjetor ora 19:00 me aktoret e njohur te skenes, si, Arben Derhemi, Alfred Trebicka, Vasjan Lami, Adelina Muca, Olta Gixhari, Laura Nezha, Niada Saliasi, Lulzim Zeqja, Eva Alikaj, Erjona Kakeli, Anila Bisha, Rajmonda Bulku, Arjola Basho, Julinda Emiri, Gert Ferra, Genti Decka, Gent Hazizi, Igli Zarka, Xhuliano Brisku. Regjisor: Mehmet Xhelili Skenografia: Genc Shkodrani Kostumet: Anila Zajmi. Rezervimet ne nr. 042223022 <span class=\"hashtag\">#ejaneteater</span> <a href=\"http://teatrikombetar.gov.al\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://teatrikombetar.gov.al</a></p>",
